snippet.title: Impaler Gold Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Impaler, the highly acclaimed minimalistic arena shooter is now covered in GOLD!! Introducing: Collectathon! A BRAND NEW MAP,  AND A COMPLETELY NEW GAME MODE. A year of regular upgrades culminates with the biggest content update yet. Shoot, slash, impale, repeat.

Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1573090/Impaler/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/impaler
or Humble Store: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/impaler

#Retrovibe #Retro #Games #Gamedevelopment #Developers #Newretro #NewGames #RetroFeel
